[I] UML modeling tool for Gnome

[T] Gaphor is an easy to use modeling environment. This means that you
[T] are able to create nice UML diagrams for documentation and to assist
[T] you with design decisions. Gaphor will help you create your applications.
[T]
[T] Gaphor has an UML 2.0 compliant data model.

[U] https://gaphor.org/

[A] Arjan Molenaar <arjanmol@users.sourceforge.net>
